725646f-a.title: Queens: 77th Street - 88th Avenue
725646f-a.text:
8801-77th Street at the southeast corner of Eighty-eight
Avenue, showing the home of Deminie CClark. This house is located
in a vicinity known as Union Course, now a section of Woodhaven.
It does not appear in any real estate atlas of GQueens county
until sometime subsequent to 1891.
1922
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
